msgctxt "56_Feather"
msgid "This ain't over, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Kiryu"
msgid "Snap out of your damn fantasy world, will you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80_Feather"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "You think by beating me you'll get some kind of super power?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104_Feather"
msgid "Uh... Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"Listen, even if you could beat me, there's no real point. At best, people "
"might think you're a pretty good fighter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Feather"
msgid "That ain't－"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Kiryu"
msgid "Just hear me out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"Do you think that kind of power alone means a thing to the rest of the "
"world? Sure, there are tons of yakuza who think as you do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"But for someone like you, who has the charisma to bring so many people "
"together, is that really what you want to dedicate your life to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176_Feather"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188_Kiryu"
msgid "That reliance on power alone－it's no different from the way yakuza think."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"Let's say you manage to get that power. The only thing waiting for you "
"after that is a power struggle with the yakuza and the mafia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"If it comes to that, a lot of your men are going to get hurt or left "
"behind. Is that really what you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224_Feather"
msgid "No... I don't want that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"Then you need to gather the ones that believe in you and find a new "
"purpose. If you can't do that, then get the hell out of Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248_Feather"
msgid "...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"Kamurocho isn't the entire world. You could make it anywhere if you decide "
"that fighting here isn't the smart choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272_Kiryu"
msgid ""
"I know because I got away from this town to make a new life in Okinawa. As "
"young as you are, you've got plenty of time to start over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284_Feather"
msgid ""
"Okay, I hear you. I'm going to disband the Phoenix. I'm not leaving "
"Kamurocho, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296_Feather"
msgid "I'm gonna live the right way, here in town. I'll show you, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Give it your best shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320_Feather"
msgid "Well... Catch ya later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380_Akaishi"
msgid ""
"Kiryu-san, I'm truly impressed! Not only did you defeat their boss, you "
"seem to have helped him become a new man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392_Akaishi"
msgid ""
"Most of the top Phoenix members showed up at a local barbershop earlier. "
"Apparently they intend to shave their heads and become monks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404_Kiryu"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416_Akaishi"
msgid ""
"Anyway, without their leader we won't have too many problems from this gang "
"anymore. He really brought the whole group together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428_Akaishi"
msgid ""
"I'm sure we don't have to worry about them starting fights after this. What "
"a relief."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440_Akaishi"
msgid "Oh, this is a token of my appreciation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464_Akaishi"
msgid "We appreciate all your help."
msgstr ""